Testerday the play was “running“ in the Supreme Court, a. Magistrate’s Court, the District At¬ torney’s office and all up and down Broadway, where it was tlie topic of topics. The first announcement that the play was to be given here appeared exclusively in The World Wednes¬ day. It was deseribed as a series of intimate episodes, in each of which a man and a woman appear. The ar¬ tigle set forth that the, play had caused rlots in Berlin, but is consid¬ ered a classic by many critics. Action followed quickly. John S.
